{"tid":1298054,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【7月8日事後檢討】被fake有野講","createTime":"2019-07-08T18:09:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T01:59:28.000Z","uid":102329,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"424ddf59d39f49f9e30a9b02804a8b8bb1d0001f","tid":1298054,"uid":102329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:09:41.000Z","msg":"首先，我係俾人fake 左出去嘅人。但我唔會因為同路人嘅一次失誤而放棄下次出黎!!<br />\n同時我認為大家要做事後檢討，從而令自己成長!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">To 推玩野post者：</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 訊息系統</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對面有完善訊息系統</span></strong>，有天眼，有人手，派一隊人去已經知流料。<br />\n相反，我地只有tg，連登呢類大平台。諗住玩對家，其實只會<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>玩到自己人</strong></span>，做成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>訊息混亂</strong></span>！<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2. 目標為本</span></span></strong><br />\n唔好花時間做損己不損人嘅事。<br />\n和理非：可以幫手做文宣、出街站、連儂牆。為下次升級打好<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意基礎</span></strong>。<br />\n勇武：做gym、操體能。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">提升身體質素</span></strong>，大大隻喺前線保護自己，同時要保護更多嘅學生。<br />\n<br />\n當然，被fake嘅我都有責任。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">To 被fake者：</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 獨立思考</span></strong></span><br />\n 連登已經放左上台，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對家會派好多人做分化、帶風向</span></strong>。所以我地要三思而行，當有唔肯定時，自己做資料搜集、做分析。凡事要諗後果，我地喺度捉緊一場很大的棋架，每一步都好重要!我地除左要行動升級，更重要嘅係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">思想升級!!!</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.  事後檢討</span></strong></span><br />\n 唔好指責同路人，要自我反省。被fake唔係問題，最重要係大家要有成長。大家要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">養成檢討嘅習慣</span></strong>(不論前線/物資運送/文宣方針)，下次要做得更好、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">更有效率</span></strong>!!<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n最後，明白有人只係想派膠放鬆心情，但係可以用其他方法嘅，例如post下寵物相。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oyd5UvQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOyd5UvQ.jpg&h=48933591&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7j17opb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7j17opb.jpg&h=6355f9ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27YEYXw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27YEYXw.jpg&h=49dfdce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化、不割蓆</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6ee67e7389567b5455913744ae1dc6f8760f23f5","tid":1298054,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:10:35.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"a0ef9a01bf062bad9db0921689b4f456039e0870","tid":1298054,"uid":232845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:11:23.000Z","msg":"Ներեցեք<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dbed6028dfda5d776344c0f2ae0f93e201433b","tid":1298054,"uid":11698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:11:39.000Z","msg":"大家已經明 好多post講緊<br />\n<code>屯門手足 唔好搞Vcity</code>"},{"pid":"673c79311135e170afd3df3803b2bc3544441730","tid":1298054,"uid":191740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"好得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060c87d36a3049d81f8979c2ee9425888f490582","tid":1298054,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5f4fa51dc3590b28a9e663463dfc171fa12caa","tid":1298054,"uid":102329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T18:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5d55a4bc4cec90479a72ecfe989c8f2db8598c","tid":1298054,"uid":152759,"like":